data.description: Introducing a stunning two-story home in Raleigh area! This elegant residence features four bedrooms & 2.5 baths, offering versatile living spaces. The fourth bedroom can also serve as a game room or extended play area, catering to various needs. The spacious family room, complete with a fireplace, provides a cozy atmosphere for relaxation. The kitchen is a chef's delight. The master bedroom is a luxurious retreat with a vaulted ceiling & en suite bathroom, featuring a separate tub & shower. Must see home!
